<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ACBr Hub</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Projeto-ACBr-Oficial/Docker/main/PHP/img/favico-acbr.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Projeto-ACBr-Oficial/Docker/main/PHP/img/background-php.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .panel {
            width: min(92vw, 720px);
            padding: 32px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: rgba(18, 26, 39, 0.88);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 32px;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 28px;
            color: #d6deeb;
        }
        .actions {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .actions a {
            display: block;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background: #333c4e;
            transition: background-color 0.25s;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .actions a:hover {
            background: #f4ad24;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="panel">
        <a href="https://projetoacbr.com.br/">
            <img class="logo" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Projeto-ACBr-Oficial/Docker/main/PHP/img/favico-acbr.png" alt="ACBr Logo">
        </a>
        <h1>ACBr Hub</h1>
        <p>Escolha entre a documentação das APIs convertidas e os demos legados.</p>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="{{ apisUrl }}">Explorar APIs</a>
            <a href="{{ demosUrl }}">Abrir Demos</a>
            <a href="{{ catalogUrl }}">Consultar Catálogo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
